Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,听广播说下午就会停了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚典礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以前一直被你妈说 音乐会要穿的正式一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 今天周日食堂没开吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:33.26,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}和奏 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
